    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330180/extras/197717dda78ff5cf8479a9d173c6423f.poster.avif?t=1750347228\" width=800 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330180/extras/197717dda78ff5cf8479a9d173c6423f.webm?t=1750347228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330180/extras/197717dda78ff5cf8479a9d173c6423f.mp4?t=1750347228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RANDOBOUNCE</strong> is a minimalistic, fast-paced, arcade, score-attack roguelike where chaos is your best weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have no control over movement, <i>just bouncing!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But you <i>do</i> have control over the firepower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build the ultimate weapon by combining multiple <strong>Barrels</strong>, each firing different types of <strong>Bullets</strong>, from homing missiles to explosive rounds. Every upgrade shapes your weapon into a unique, enemy-shredding machine. Tweak individual stats, from the <i>Fire Rate</i>, to the <i>Rotation</i> of each Barrel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330180/extras/c4761c78c9ddaea0f0d355e8826b1b50.poster.avif?t=1750347228\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330180/extras/c4761c78c9ddaea0f0d355e8826b1b50.webm?t=1750347228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330180/extras/c4761c78c9ddaea0f0d355e8826b1b50.mp4?t=1750347228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive for 20 minutes while racking up the highest score possible. Along the way, collect <strong>Power-Ups</strong> that provide game-changing <i>offensive</i> and <i>defensive</i> perks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330180/extras/b8729dc675bad6e83a6bdecfcaf85944.poster.avif?t=1750347228\" width=800 height=504 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330180/extras/b8729dc675bad6e83a6bdecfcaf85944.webm?t=1750347228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330180/extras/b8729dc675bad6e83a6bdecfcaf85944.mp4?t=1750347228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>But remember, you are at the mercy of bouncing!</i></p>",
